@startuml
actor User
participant "Aplikasi" as App
participant "Google OAuth" as Google
participant "Sistem" as System
participant "Database" as DB

User -> App : Membuka aplikasi
User -> App : Klik "Login dengan Google"

App -> Google : Redirect ke Google OAuth
Google -> User : Tampilkan halaman izin akses\n(Akun Google)

User -> Google : Pilih akun & Beri izin
Google --> App : Kirim Authorization Code

App -> System : Kirim Authorization Code
System -> Google : Request Access Token
Google --> System : Access Token + User Info

System -> DB : Validasi/Registrasi user\n(Cari user berdasarkan email Google)
DB --> System : Data user ditemukan / baru dibuat

System --> App : Login berhasil
App -> User : Tampilkan Dashboard

@enduml
